725045f-a.title: Queens: 15th Avenue - 149th Street
725045f-a.text:
Fifteenth Ave. (old 16th Street), north side, between 149th Street
(Seventh Ave.) and 150th Street (Eighth Ave.), showing a station of the
north side division of the Long Island Railroad in Whitestone. This is
a set of two views.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
